Any local sponsoring community desiring to qualify for funding, must:
Make application to the cabinet which shall be in the form and manner prescribed by the cabinet;
Provide at no expense to the cabinet, all lands and easements necessary for project construction;
Agree to operate and maintain the project in a manner acceptable to the Commonwealth to insure the continued capacity of the project to prevent or minimize flood damages;
Submit evidence of the history of flooding within the last five (5) years;
Submit evidence of flood damage in dollars within the last five (5) years.
